Parts List 
---------- 
  
U1 - Texas Instruments TCM1506 
T1 - 4000:8 ohm audio transfomer 
S1 - 8 ohm speaker 
R1 - 2.2k resistor 
R2 - External variable resistor; adjusts timing frequency 
C1 - .47uF capacitor 
C2 - .1uF capacitor 
C3 - 10uF capacitor 
L1 - Tip 
L2 - Ring 
     L1 and L2 are the phone line. 
  
  
